    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与曾经伟大仁慈、如今却被遗忘的神明踏上征程，他的神力正从世界中慢慢流逝。被野心勃勃的人类弟子背叛——这个弟子企图通过献祭师父来获得神位，神明起初对人类心怀不信，直到亲眼目睹他们在黑暗中英勇抗争。在消逝于虚无之前，神明决定最后一次拯救人类。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >序章版内容</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - 第一章5个关卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - 约60分钟游戏时长</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - 5个角色阶段中开放2个 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拥抱指挥官的角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 率领勇敢的冒险者团队，征战被黑暗侵蚀的末世战场。在精心设计的回合制战斗中历练四个扣人心弦的章节，看着菜鸟新兵蜕变为身经百战的勇士。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327980/extras/5921a819f977b3d5db7dbf45e4c25157.poster.avif?t=1771251694\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327980/extras/5921a819f977b3d5db7dbf45e4c25157.webm?t=1771251694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327980/extras/5921a819f977b3d5db7dbf45e4c25157.mp4?t=1771251694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >运用您的战略和战术技能</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 发挥战略战术才能考验你的指挥智慧，在战术对抗中运筹帷幄，制定作战方案，发动致命攻势，努力扭转战局。见证你的杂牌军逐步成长为传奇英雄，从默默无闻走向神话传说。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327980/extras/fee93c549ffa08763ad8aba888ec16b8.poster.avif?t=1771251694\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327980/extras/fee93c549ffa08763ad8aba888ec16b8.webm?t=1771251694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327980/extras/fee93c549ffa08763ad8aba888ec16b8.mp4?t=1771251694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建立您的新兵小队</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 悉心投资团队建设，精心培养队员的技能和意志力，让他们能够承受前路的残酷考验。每个选择都举足轻重，你需要在绝望的危机中开辟出希望之光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327980/extras/3150176eb8f9aea0acaec80738971cd4.webp?t=1771251694\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327980/extras/3150176eb8f9aea0acaec80738971cd4.poster.avif?t=1771251694\" class=\"bb_img\" width=1170 height=488 /></picture></span></p>",
